1
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:02,820
=The Unexpected Marriage=

2
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:07,660
=Episode 5=

3
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,870
Here, Young Master.

4
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:28,070
Young Master.

5
00:02:28,230 --> 00:02:29,070
Do you want more?

6
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,510
Bring them all.

7
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:31,470
It's all here.

8
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:46,740
(Luck and Blessing)

9
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:52,000
Young Master is smart.

10
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,390
You let us lure Zhao Huaibi

11
00:02:54,390 --> 00:02:56,120
to Muyan Forest.

12
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,350
This chance encounter

13
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:59,470
will definitely change Her Highness's mind

14
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:00,540
and make her fall for Zhao Huaibi.

15
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:02,460
Zhao Huaibi has made outstanding
military achievements.

16
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:04,070
I believe we can get more information

17
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:06,070
about Fuyu from him.

18
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,240
It's better to use hot water.

19
00:03:27,510 --> 00:03:28,630
Princess Guangde.

20
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,870
How did she leave?

21
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,550
Why is she acting weird lately?

22
00:03:36,550 --> 00:03:37,870
According to her previous temper,

23
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,630
she should've come to provoke you now.

24
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:43,440
Maybe it's because you helped her
at the Lantern Festival

25
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,520
so she changed her attitude.

26
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:48,070
Maybe.

27
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,870
Your Highness, we found out.

28
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,320
The reason why Princess Guangde

29
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,160
changed her temperament drastically

30
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,590
is because of a man.

31
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:59,630
So where is my destined man?

32
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:01,950
Yours hasn't appeared yet.

33
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:04,030
But hers has shown up.

34
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:07,470
Who said mine hasn't appeared?

35
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,520
In the deep pit accident that night,

36
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,920
my destined man

37
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,110
already appeared.

38
00:04:13,110 --> 00:04:13,950
Who is it?

39
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,160
Zhao Huaibi.

40
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,000
General Zhao.

41
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:19,920
Well...

42
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:22,720
She just has someone she likes.

43
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,200
Which man does she fancy?

44
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,600
I don't know.

45
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,670
I only know that they met
at the Lantern Festival.

46
00:04:29,110 --> 00:04:30,590
That man rescued her.

47
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,080
Princess Guangde

48
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,160
couldn't forget him since then.

49
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,880
Your Highness.

50
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,720
What a small world.

51
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:42,600
I did not expect

52
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,110
our fate

53
00:04:44,670 --> 00:04:46,350
is tied to one person.

54
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:47,190
Who?

55
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,120
Zhao Huaibi,

56
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,270
General Zhao.

57
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:51,320
You mean the General Zhao

58
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,030
who hasn't yet returned to the capital?

59
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,470
Your Highness.

60
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:55,470
Be careful.

61
00:04:55,470 --> 00:04:57,080
Don't tell Princess Guangde.

62
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,750
You need to take action first.

63
00:04:58,750 --> 00:04:59,590
Take action first.

64
00:05:01,350 --> 00:05:02,200
Your Highness.

65
00:05:02,290 --> 00:05:03,530
Princess Guangde requests to meet you.

66
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,360
Princess.

67
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:12,310
Speak of the devil.

68
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,160
Changsheng.

69
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,320
What brought

70
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,880
you here today?

71
00:05:22,790 --> 00:05:25,480
These are the storybooks I carefully prepared.

72
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,720
Many good love stories are recorded.

73
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,520
Read them and accumulate some experience.

74
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,110
Come, sit down first.

75
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:38,320
Are they really useful?

76
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,880
Of course.

77
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:41,080
Moreover,

78
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,470
if one of us gets married first,

79
00:05:42,470 --> 00:05:44,590
she'll get rid of the peace-making marriage.

80
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,430
Although we are opponents,

81
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,990
we still need to be fair.

82
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:50,280
I don't want to cheat.

83
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,080
Thanks.

84
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,640
Alright,

85
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,400
I'm not used to this yet.

86
00:05:57,790 --> 00:05:58,910
I'm telling you,

87
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,590
I think this matter

88
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,080
is not as difficult

89
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,110
as we think.

90
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,560
It's either

91
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,960
quarrelsome lovers

92
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,880
or

93
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,760
childhood sweethearts.

94
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:09,390
First, the two people were at odds.

95
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,880
Then their fates entangle.

96
00:06:11,110 --> 00:06:12,680
If there's no fate,

97
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,280
we can create opportunities ourselves.

98
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,640
Just pester him.

99
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:17,110
- If pestering doesn't work...
- Guangde.

100
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,790
We are rivals.

101
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,280
I know.

102
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:24,790
But it has to be fair.

103
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,200
Don't worry.

104
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,400
Even if we like the same person,

105
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,520
I won't mind.

106
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:33,310
Really?

107
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,470
I really don't mind.

108
00:06:37,230 --> 00:06:38,640
Wait.

109
00:06:38,990 --> 00:06:41,320
What do you mean by "really"?

110
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,960
Guangde.

111
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,790
Since you're here to deliver the notes

112
00:06:47,790 --> 00:06:48,840
and share everything you know,

113
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,870
then I will also be honest.

114
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:51,880
Actually

115
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,160
that day at the Lantern Festival,

116
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:55,110
the person you met is...

117
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,990
Who is it?

118
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:00,030
Tell me quickly.

119
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,520
It's Zhao Huaibi.

120
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:04,720
General Zhao.

121
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:06,270
Really?

122
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,920
No.

123
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,470
Wait a minute.

124
00:07:12,110 --> 00:07:14,030
You mean...

125
00:07:16,350 --> 00:07:17,910
He also saved me after that.

126
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:22,430
You're saying

127
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,350
he saved you...

128
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:29,390
Hurry up.

129
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,470
Take all of these away.

130
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,430
Don't leave any.

131
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:34,230
Didn't you say you wanted it to be fair?

132
00:07:35,670 --> 00:07:37,750
Who wants to be fair to you?

133
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,040
I didn't say that.

134
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,960
Give me this one back, too.

135
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,000
Go.

136
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:49,840
In terms of talent and appearance,

137
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:52,280
you're the best in Shangkang.

138
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,000
But my Guangde

139
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,200
is also beautiful

140
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,520
and intelligent.

141
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,390
You two

142
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:00,030
are a match made in heaven.

143
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,000
How about I issue a decree

144
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,320
and make you two

145
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,670
a couple?

146
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:05,750
Your Majesty,

147
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,910
thank you for your kindness.

148
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:08,520
It's just

149
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,720
I have a disability.

150
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,200
I'm not good enough

151
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,160
for Princess Guangde.

152
00:08:12,790 --> 00:08:13,640
So I dare not agree.

153
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,760
You dare not agree

154
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,760
or you don't want to?

155
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:20,120
You've used this reason many times.

156
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,710
I also have my pride.

157
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:22,590
All right?

158
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:27,200
I noticed that your leg

159
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,160
is no different from ordinary people's.

160
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,830
Are you using the crutch

161
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,800
just to refuse the marriage?

162
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,640
I dare not.

163
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:34,760
My official rank

164
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,960
is low.

165
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:38,030
In terms of ability, I have
no military achievements.

166
00:08:38,430 --> 00:08:39,950
It's just unjustifiable.

167
00:08:40,190 --> 00:08:41,950
If I do marry Princess Guangde,

168
00:08:41,950 --> 00:08:44,000
I'm afraid it will make the royal family
a laughing stock.

169
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,120
If this is true,

170
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:49,670
please execute me, Your Majesty.

171
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,790
You'd rather die than marry Guangde?

172
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:56,470
Wouldn't that make me a tyrant?

173
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:57,830
Being a matchmaker

174
00:08:57,830 --> 00:08:59,870
is harder than being the Emperor.

175
00:08:59,870 --> 00:09:01,400
I need to persuade everyone earnestly

176
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,880
for their marriage.

177
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,120
Never mind.

178
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:07,430
I won't interfere.

179
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:08,430
Thank you, Your Majesty.

180
00:09:08,430 --> 00:09:15,430
(Imperial Study)

181
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,120
Xiao Zilv.

182
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:20,120
You would rather die than marry me.

183
00:09:21,310 --> 00:09:22,710
Princess, please calm down.

184
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:23,560
I...

185
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,400
Well done.

186
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:27,190
Actually, I already have someone I like.

187
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:29,080
You must stand your ground.

188
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,480
Next time, don't just talk.

189
00:09:32,190 --> 00:09:33,360
Princess, what are you doing?

190
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,360
Don't be afraid.

191
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,040
I'm afraid that next time
my father will force you.

192
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,590
You can't just talk.

193
00:09:37,590 --> 00:09:38,790
You need to take action.

194
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:40,670
This dagger

195
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:42,120
is extremely sharp,

196
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,360
which can cut clean through iron.

197
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,560
If it really doesn't work,

198
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,910
just cut it off.

199
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,550
I'm the only son in the family.

200
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,960
What are you thinking?

201
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,990
Lecher.

202
00:09:51,990 --> 00:09:53,120
I mean cut your leg.

203
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,230
If it still doesn't work,

204
00:09:58,230 --> 00:09:59,600
cut off both legs.

205
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:01,710
I don't believe Father is still so persistent.

206
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,280
Princess, you deserve

207
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,590
a hero in the world.

208
00:10:08,590 --> 00:10:09,790
Actually,

209
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,590
the man I like

210
00:10:11,590 --> 00:10:12,880
is indeed a hero.

211
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:14,680
It's just

212
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,550
Changsheng also likes him.

213
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,480
What do you think I should do?

214
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,630
Princess, if you don't mind,

215
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,960
I am willing to lend you

216
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,950
a helping hand.

217
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,920
You want to help me

218
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,430
or help yourself?

219
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:29,080
You are always against Changsheng.

220
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,190
Do you want to marry her?

221
00:10:38,430 --> 00:10:39,270
Jin.

222
00:10:39,310 --> 00:10:40,150
Are you embroidering?

223
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:43,710
This pattern is obviously not for me.

224
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,310
Humph.

225
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,830
You look very happy today.

226
00:10:48,310 --> 00:10:50,280
Today is really refreshing.

227
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,080
You argued with Changsheng again?

228
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,070
No.

229
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:55,990
This time I am

230
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:57,430
sitting back and reaping the benefits.

231
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,680
If Changsheng is the snipe,

232
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,880
who is that clam?

233
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,430
Guangde.

234
00:11:03,430 --> 00:11:05,070
You're helping Guangde against Changsheng?

235
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,070
Don't tell her.

236
00:11:07,070 --> 00:11:08,280
Zilv.

237
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:10,830
How can you bear
to watch Changsheng marry far away?

238
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:13,360
Rest assured.

239
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,710
I know you are close to Changsheng.

240
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,830
If she is really forced to marry far away,

241
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:18,590
I'll just open my arms

242
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:20,030
and marry her.

243
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,720
See you.

244
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:30,190
My brother just got close to her

245
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,310
and then broke a leg.

246
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,240
If he marries Changsheng...

247
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,840
No.

248
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:35,760
No way.

249
00:11:37,430 --> 00:11:38,270
Changsheng.

250
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,670
Jin.

251
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,680
How did you come?

252
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,830
I sneaked out.

253
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:44,070
Got to go back soon.

254
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:45,830
What's so important?

255
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:47,040
I heard from my brother

256
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,310
that you like Zhao Huaibi?

257
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:50,950
General Zhao is going to go fishing tomorrow.

258
00:11:51,190 --> 00:11:52,520
You should prepare early.

259
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,310
Don't let Zhao Huaibi marry Guangde.

260
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:56,910
Jin, you are still the best to me.

261
00:11:58,310 --> 00:12:00,160
If I really can't get married,

262
00:12:00,430 --> 00:12:01,670
I'll marry your brother.

263
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,990
Anyway,

264
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:04,160
he has already broken a leg.

265
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,360
There shouldn't be any more problems.

266
00:12:05,830 --> 00:12:06,830
Marry my brother?

267
00:12:06,830 --> 00:12:07,710
No way.

268
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,000
No.

269
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,840
Well...

270
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:13,590
My brother

271
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:14,920
is actually an

272
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:15,950
embroidered pillow,

273
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,440
pleasant to the eye but of no use.

274
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,680
Usually, he looks

275
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,160
elegant on the outside,

276
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,510
but he's terrible

277
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,360
behind people's backs.

278
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:24,400
You don't know, Changsheng.

279
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,240
How could I not know?

280
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:27,830
Don't worry.

281
00:12:28,830 --> 00:12:29,830
I won't choose

282
00:12:29,830 --> 00:12:31,190
Xiao Zilv to be my husband.

283
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:33,440
Even if I have to marry into Great Tang,

284
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,600
I won't consider him.

285
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,000
But

286
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,360
I don't want you to go to Great Tang.

287
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:41,400
Thank you, Jin.

288
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:43,790
Then I'll leave first.

289
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,310
Wait a minute, Jin.

290
00:12:45,310 --> 00:12:47,070
We've got a batch of fruits you like.

291
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:48,280
Take some away.

292
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:50,470
No, I'll come to your house to eat next time.

293
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:51,310
Bye.

294
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:11,190
Why are you sighing?

295
00:13:11,470 --> 00:13:12,760
