878
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,320
People can take care of each other

879
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,550
and also attack together.

880
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:47,230
There are many subtle changes in the formation.

881
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:48,670
Impressive.

882
00:37:54,590 --> 00:37:55,430
Princess.

883
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:56,800
If you step on

884
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,240
this pedal firmly,

885
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:59,830
the other foot kicks off the ground,

886
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,480
then you can jump on the horse's back.

887
00:38:02,470 --> 00:38:03,310
Okay.

888
00:38:05,240 --> 00:38:07,390
One foot step on it.

889
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:10,950
Zhao.

890
00:38:10,950 --> 00:38:12,240
You are so far away from me.

891
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:14,430
What if I accidentally fall down?

892
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:16,000
I will get injured.

893
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,830
Then I'll hold the horse.

894
00:38:42,030 --> 00:38:42,870
Princess.

895
00:38:42,950 --> 00:38:44,040
Are you hurt?

896
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:46,070
I apologize.

897
00:38:46,070 --> 00:38:47,600
I accidentally made you fall.

898
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:51,710
Let's continue practicing.

899
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:54,120
Get on the horse and give me a hand.

900
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:55,520
I...

901
00:38:56,590 --> 00:38:57,600
All right.

902
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:08,640
Pull me up.

903
00:39:17,470 --> 00:39:18,440
Well...

904
00:39:19,030 --> 00:39:19,870
Princess.

905
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:22,270
Give me the reins.

906
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:25,560
Here.

907
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:28,640
Princess.

908
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:30,640
I...

909
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,240
I'm just protecting you.

910
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:33,600
I don't have any frivolous intention.

911
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:53,880
Have you eaten enough?

912
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:54,720
Let's go.

913
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:08,110
Princess, rest assured.

914
00:40:08,110 --> 00:40:09,390
I will protect you well.

915
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,240
Zhao.

916
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,680
Let's go out for a walk.

917
00:40:23,680 --> 00:40:24,520
Okay.

918
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,160
General.

919
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:45,510
In addition to

920
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:47,320
fishing and horse riding,

921
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:48,710
do you have any other hobbies?

922
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,120
Usually

923
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:51,680
I just practice martial arts and read books.

924
00:40:51,680 --> 00:40:52,760
Reading?

925
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:53,840
Reading is good.

926
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,280
I also like reading books.

927
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:57,350
I'm currently learning how to write a book.

928
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,960
What books do you usually read?

929
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:01,990
I prefer to read

930
00:41:01,990 --> 00:41:03,040
Sun Tzu's The Art of War.

931
00:41:03,430 --> 00:41:04,350
Do you know that?

932
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:08,070
I've heard of Sun Tzu.

933
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:09,480
But Art of War?

934
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,790
It's enough that I understand you.

935
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,160
Princess.

936
00:41:19,550 --> 00:41:20,560
I'm a rough man,

937
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,190
and don't know much

938
00:41:22,190 --> 00:41:23,320
about love.

939
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,190
It's okay.

940
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:26,030
And it's not that you know nothing about it.

941
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:27,640
You just don't want to understand it now.

942
00:41:28,240 --> 00:41:29,390
But that's okay.

943
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:31,120
I can wait for you.

944
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:33,840
As long as you want,

945
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:35,040
I can wait forever

946
00:41:35,470 --> 00:41:37,800
until one day

947
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,510
you and I can be together

948
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:40,440
and enjoy a carefree life.

949
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,280
What do you say?

950
00:41:41,630 --> 00:41:43,000
A carefree life.

951
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:56,920
Your Highness, you're discouraged?

952
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,200
Yi'an.

953
00:41:59,510 --> 00:42:00,600
Are you married?

954
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,920
I'm alone.

955
00:42:04,470 --> 00:42:05,750
Do you have someone you like?

956
00:42:07,510 --> 00:42:08,520
Someone I like?

957
00:42:10,070 --> 00:42:10,910
It's not in a hurry.

958
00:42:11,470 --> 00:42:12,830
Didn't you say that

959
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:15,080
love is fated?

960
00:42:15,990 --> 00:42:17,360
Guangde said

961
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:18,670
it's easiest to write

962
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:20,230
storybooks about love.

963
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:22,230
Innocence and intimacy

964
00:42:22,470 --> 00:42:23,560
of childhood sweethearts,

965
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,440
finding each other congenial

966
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,520
and making solemn vows.

967
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,350
Your Highness.

968
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,360
If Princess Guangde said that,

969
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,560
maybe it makes some sense.

970
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:32,950
Look.

971
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,240
General Zhao

972
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:35,830
has been tamed by Guangde.

973
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:38,080
It seems so.

974
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:51,190
So you will choose to give up?

975
00:42:52,150 --> 00:42:53,080
I won't.

976
00:42:55,590 --> 00:42:56,430
Yi'an.

977
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:58,080
You will help me, right?

978
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,270
What are you doing?

979
00:43:07,200 --> 00:43:08,040
I accepted it.

980
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:24,870
It's snowing.

981
00:43:34,470 --> 00:43:36,440
(The world is troubled by love.)

982
00:43:37,030 --> 00:43:38,030
(But it's the same)

983
00:43:38,030 --> 00:43:39,080
(whether you get it or not.)

984
00:43:39,950 --> 00:43:41,040
(Gains and losses)

985
00:43:41,720 --> 00:43:43,390
(are all experiences in life.)

986
00:44:09,030 --> 00:44:14,100
Sitting alone in the west window,
quietly watching the snow

987
00:44:15,630 --> 00:44:21,720
Silently falling and piling up

988
00:44:22,380 --> 00:44:28,550
The red flowers can't stand the cold

989
00:44:29,840 --> 00:44:34,460
And withered at night

990
00:44:35,760 --> 00:44:41,030
Facing the freezing north wind

991
00:44:42,240 --> 00:44:48,690
Looking at you, it's hard to say goodbye

992
00:44:49,050 --> 00:44:55,650
I fear the heat will fade away in an instant

993
00:44:56,430 --> 00:45:02,640
The snow covers the night

994
00:45:04,750 --> 00:45:11,170
After the separation, it's hard to meet again

995
00:45:11,470 --> 00:45:17,960
Can't see through the ups and downs of fate

996
00:45:18,110 --> 00:45:25,010
Let the yearning for you run wild

997
00:45:25,620 --> 00:45:31,480
How can a lonely lamp comfort me

998
00:45:31,810 --> 00:45:38,560
The sky is dark, the moon is waning

999
00:45:38,990 --> 00:45:45,850
Hear my cry

1000
00:46:01,770 --> 00:46:06,410
You're wearing a blue gown

1001
00:46:09,030 --> 00:46:14,770
Spring breeze blowing

1002
00:46:16,130 --> 00:46:21,860
Another year has passed
